text: Hasan Mohamed Hasan Ali Al-Moharrami (Arabic:حسن المحرمي) (born 6 June 1996) is an Emirati international footballer who plays as a defender for Emirati club Baniyas. ==External links== * * ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Emirati footballers Category:People from Abu Dhabi Category:Association football defenders Category:Baniyas Club players Category:UAE Pro League players Category:UAE First Division League players Category:United Arab Emirates international footballers
